                "name": "Fight Common Enemy",
                "description": "Determine the outcome of a non-boss combat encounter.\r\n\r\n- **Energy**: Make sure the robot has at least 1 to start.\r\n- **Difficulty:** If you're significantly outleveled, for example level 1 or 2 to the enemy's 5, then set difficulty to *Hard*. If you significantly outlevel the opponent, then set difficulty to *Easy*, although that is probably a good time to move on to the next location.\r\n\r\nRoll, then see [Finish Fight](/play/event/18?subject_id=13).",
